reviewText:
should've had MUCH more content for the money.

I am kinda disappointed both with the overview sections and the recordings.

I was looking for material for a voice class I will be teaching this fall.  This was one of the pieces of literature I was reviewing.  It was not what I needed.  It was more for church  or spiritual music.  I know it said worship in the title but sometimes that means little if the info is presented well.  This was not something I would use.  I was looking for texts for high school.
